OL,3,CWoman found dead in Stoke-on-Trent
OL,4,Cnamed by police
OL,6,FA woman who was found dead in Stoke-on-
OL,7,FTrent has been named by police.
OL,9,FStaffordshire Police were called to an
OL,10,Faddress in Oakwell Court, in Longton,
OL,11,Fat around 3.30am on Sunday, 12 July.
OL,13,FThe body of a woman was found inside.
OL,14,FOfficers have now confirm the woman to
OL,15,Fbe 24-year-old Sarah-Louise
OL,16,FPennington, from Stoke-on-Trent.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
