OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784033312
OL,3,CWoman found dead in Stoke-on-Trent
OL,4,Cnamed by police
OL,6,FA 30-year-old man from Stoke-on-Trent
OL,7,Fwho was arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fmurder remains in custody and will
OL,9,Fcontinue to be questioned after extra
OL,10,Ftime was granted.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Kirsty Oldfield
OL,13,Fsaid: "We're working incredibly hard
OL,14,Fto progress our lines of enquiry into
OL,15,Fthis investigation and to support the
OL,16,Fwoman's family at such a traumatic
OL,17,Ftime.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
