OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784033312
OL,3,CWoman found dead in Stoke-on-Trent
OL,4,Cnamed by police
OL,6,F"We know the outer cordon is affecting
OL,7,Fa lot of residents' access to their
OL,8,Fhomes and we are working to reduce the
OL,9,Fsize of the cordon as soon as we can."
OL,11,F"I'd like to reassure the community
OL,12,Fthat we are not currently seeking
OL,13,Fanyone else in connection with this
OL,14,Finvestigation and our enquiries are
OL,15,Fmoving at pace.
OL,17,F"Officers will be out carrying out
OL,18,Fhouse-to-house enquiries and providing
OL,19,Fvisible reassurance in the area.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@fO]sD@AOUyD@AOU
